'3. From the directory where you added the configuration file, clone the the AzureML-'
'Examples repository 2 .'
'Bash'
'git clone https://githu.com/Azure/azureml-examples.git -- depth 1'
'4. Start the noteook server from the directory, which now contains the clone and'
'the config file.'
'Bash'
'jupyter noteook'
